## ğŸ“Š Project Overview

The goal is to identify which features (such as **alcohol**, **acidity**, and **sulphates**) most strongly influence wine quality.  
The model achieved an **RÂ² â‰ˆ 0.33**, indicating moderate explanatory power and suggesting some nonlinear effects may exist.

