## ğŸ§¾ Model Summary
- **Model:** `quality ~ alcohol + volatile_acidity + sulphates + citric_acid + density`
- **Significant Variables:**  
  - âœ… `alcohol` (positive)  
  - âœ… `sulphates` (positive)  
  - âŒ `volatile_acidity` (negative)
- **VIF check:** All < 5 (no strong multicollinearity)  
- **Residuals:** roughly normal and homoscedastic

